Address:
Town'N Country Mobile Home Park
Send your inquiries to:
Attention: Office Manager
4425 US-441 South
Okeechobee, FL
34974
Directions
From North
- Take Forida's Turnpike South toward Miami.
Take Exit 193 for US-441 South. Stay on US-441 all the way to Okeechobee. 
US-441 will merge with US-98 S, continue approx. 2.8 miles. Turn Right into 
Town'N Country Mobile Home Park
From West
- Take FL-70 E toward Okeechobee. 
FL-70 will merge with US-98, continue for approx 1 mile. Turn Right onto US-98/US-441. 
In approx 2.8 miles, Turn Right into Town'N Country Mobile Home Park

#BeginEditable "body1"
About Us
Town'N Country Mobile Home Park is a beautiful, quiet, seniors only (55+) 
		community located on the northern tip of Lake Okeechobee in southern 
		Florida - off of HWY 441. We are located less than 2 hours south of Disney World!
The community was established in 1972 with over 170 original lots. In 
		2018 the community was purchased by the new owners and the renovations 
		began, including 7 newly developed lots.
Lake Okeechobee is the 2nd largest natural lake in the US. It is 
		known as the "Crappie Capital" of the south and has some of the best 
		bass fishing you will find in Florida.
Office hours: Mon-Fri 9:00am - 12:00pm, Closed 
		holidays
Okeechobee, FL is centrally located in southern Florida - only 50 
		minutes from the east coast of Florida and 75 minutes from the west 
		coast. To the east you will find Vero Beach, Port St. Lucie and West 
		Palm Beach. To the west is Sarasota, Fort Meyers and Cape Coral.
#EndEditable
